title: I’m Ready For A Family She’s Not
itunes:title: I’m Ready For A Family She’s Not
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I’m 27 years old and I have my degree in business management, with aspirations of owning a business one day and I’m on the right path to fulfill my goals. I’ve been dating a woman for a few months and she was everything I asked God for. She’s a go getter with a lot of ambition and a backbone. She’s not a pushover by any means and she has a foul mouth when I make her mad...............
